<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to <%= appName %>!</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f9; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%); padding: 48px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header img { height: 40px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .text { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 8px 0 24px; }
    .steps { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .steps h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .step { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .step-num { background: #6366f1; color: #fff; width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 12px; margin-top: 1px; }
    .step-text { font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.5; }
    .step-text strong { color: #1a1a2e; }
    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 32px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 24px 40px; background: #f8fafc; text-align: center; }
    .social-links { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .social-links a { display: inline-block; margin: 0 8px; color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
    .footer-text { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <% if (logoUrl) { %>
        <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="<%= appName %> logo" />
      <% } %>
      <h1>Welcome to <%= appName %>! 🎉</h1>
      <p>We're thrilled to have you on board.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p class="greeting">Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>

      <p class="text">
        Thank you for joining <strong><%= appName %></strong>! Your account has been successfully created
        on <strong><%= registeredAt %></strong>. We can't wait for you to explore everything we have to offer.
      </p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta-btn">Go to Your Dashboard →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="steps">
        <h3>Get started in 3 easy steps</h3>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-text"><strong>Complete your profile</strong> — Add your details so we can personalize your experience.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-text"><strong>Explore the dashboard</strong> — Discover all the features available to you.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-text"><strong>Invite your team</strong> — Collaboration is better together. Bring your colleagues aboard.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text">
        If you have any questions or need help getting started, our support team is always here for you.
        Just reply to this email or visit our help center.
      </p>

      <p class="text">
        Welcome aboard,<br />
        <strong>The <%= appName %> Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" style="margin: 0;" />

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#">Twitter</a>
        <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-text">
        You received this email because you signed up for <%= appName %>.<br />
        © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
